{"tid":2062865,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Community又贏］經典美劇《六人行》「都是白人」惹種族歧視爭議！特別篇恐生變","createTime":"2020-06-13T12:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:04:53.000Z","uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4387abeb4cc0057213aca34cf833466ee1e3824b","tid":2062865,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:39:29.000Z","msg":"近期美國因為警察執法失當，造成美籍非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）身亡，讓長期存在的種族歧視問題大爆發。先是奧斯卡經典名劇《亂世佳人》被下架，現在連經典美劇《Friends 六人行》也被點名，因劇中主角「清一色白人」引起紛爭，該劇製片現身電視節目淚崩致歉，而原本預計秋天上映的特別篇也恐生變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《六人行》主演都是白人，被點名歧視。（翻攝自影集劇照）<br />\n<br />\n由珍妮佛安妮斯頓（Jennifer Aniston）、麗莎庫卓（Lisa Kudrow）等人主演的美劇《Friends 六人行》，堪稱經典不敗的戲劇之一，自1994年首播以來就大受歡迎，除了劇情受到討論，就連演員穿搭也被視為流行，像是寬鬆男友襯衫、破牛仔褲、蕾絲頸鍊等，甚至是現今看來也「很可以」！"},{"pid":"59482b1cd1bfac079604868d6a819af9be16cf32","tid":2062865,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"全部冇黑人既戲由頭拍過啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187a8d0784ad2f8c69750c69c70caba6c8109c8d","tid":2062865,"uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家準備好之後嗰幾年啲劇全部都有黑人又同性戀又剩未"},{"pid":"61af7b4db757abf06bff80e32e37d8e15d96d4e5","tid":2062865,"uid":34765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"lgbt塔利班死全家啦"},{"pid":"3354368d583f290e90697ff82660acd3738b557c","tid":2062865,"uid":262914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"痴鳩線"},{"pid":"fc57f9012814fdbc3fe16dfb219014677e82e1da","tid":2062865,"uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wvZYLeD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwvZYLeD.jpg&h=2a17b01a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7414bd7cb2836e3ab5fc7602f586000eb8d1eaa","tid":206